{"tid":231034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"( 濕疹絲打入)  濕疹好痕點算好？","createTime":"2017-05-05T18:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T18:38:55.000Z","uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7bff3fd8c55d91bc2a3a19e3cff05f63a9ed9b1","tid":231034,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:16:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小女原本是沒有濕疹<br />\n但之前係外國讀書 由於天氣太乾 我又沖勁熱熱水涼 最後就開始起濕疹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老味 好生唔生 生係胸下面 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始我都on99唔知道 以為皮膚敏感 狂r同冇睇醫生 <br />\n點知....<br />\n到我返到香港 開始feel到唔對路 <br />\n因為開始有色素沉澱 我就去睇皮膚科醫生 查完類固醇係好返...但只係暫時性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家我帶bra 會勁唔舒服 扎住濕疹個位 <br />\n周不時仲會返發<br />\n真係好撚核突 同 好撚痕呀<br />\n有冇濕疹絲打有類似問題？求分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980fa00049b2018ec7c7f012685373cee0ce1cf0","tid":231034,"uid":94176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:19:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/165585/page/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/165585/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"0c2989ce14d9a212811b03f7e9ea30c2671a8440","tid":231034,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"搽類固醇？搽左幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n今次你死得，小小色素走去搽毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df74fed14a6a37ade0c285f4594a09004c6d2f71","tid":231034,"uid":13559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T18:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搽類固醇？搽左幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n今次你死得，小小色素走去搽毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搽左一個星期度 其實依個情況已經維持左年幾 我試左好多方法都唔得 好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/n